{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"@","kind":"attribute"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM","text":"MainActor","kind":"attribute"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSRadioPicker","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"<","kind":"text"},{"text":"Tag","kind":"genericParameter"},{"text":"> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"where","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Tag","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" : ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:SH","text":"Hashable","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"kind":"mentions","mentions":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/Controls"]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Accessibility considerations","anchor":"Accessibility-considerations"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Voice Over","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" will use several elements to describe the component: if component disabled \/ read only, if error context, the label and helper texts and a custom radio trait."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The picker itself does no have any defined accessiiblity value, label or identifier ; it remains in the users hands to define which one will be used."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"However if defined in the "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioPickerData","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" the items inside the picker will have such accessibility identifiers."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Forbidden by design","anchor":"Forbidden-by-design"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The design system does not allow to have "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" in both an error situation and a read only state."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The design system does not allow to have "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" in both an error situation and a disabled state."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The design system does not allow to have "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" in both a read only and a disabled state."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Code samples","anchor":"Code-samples"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["    \/\/ Define the elements to display in radio buttons using OUDSRadioPickerData.","    \/\/ This object has the same properties as the OUDSRadioItem,","    \/\/ and some of them are optional withdefault values set","    var someDataToPopulate: [OUDSRadioPickerData<String>] {","        [","            OUDSRadioPickerData<String>(tag: \"Choice_1\",","                                        label: \"Virgin Holy Lava\",","                                        extraLabel: \"Very spicy\",","                                        description: \"No alcohol, only tasty flavors\",","                                        icon: Image(systemName: \"flame\")),","","            OUDSRadioPickerData<String>(tag: \"Choice_2\",","                                        label: \"IPA beer\",","                                        description: \"From Brewdog company\",","                                        icon: Image(systemName: \"dog.fill\")),","","            OUDSRadioPickerData<String>(tag: \"Choice_3\",","                                        label: \"Mineral water\",","                                        icon: Image(systemName: \"waterbottle.fill\")),","        ]","    }","","    \/\/ Prepare the selection, with a value previously selected","    \/\/ Use the data and the binding for the picker.","    @State var selection: String = \"Choice_1\"","","    \/\/ Here the picker is vertical","    OUDSRadioPicker(selection: $selection, radios: someDataToPopulate)","","    \/\/ The picker can apply some settings to all its radio buttons.","    \/\/ It can be also horitzontal with a scroll indicator.","    \/\/ Here all the the radio buttons are in read only mode and use reversed layout.","    OUDSRadioPicker(selection: $selection,","                    radios: someDataToPopulate,","                    isReversed: true,","                    isReadOnly: true,","                    placement: .horitzontal(true))"]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Design documentation","anchor":"Design-documentation"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"There is no online specification as this component is not an official OUDS one"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Theme rendering","anchor":"Theme-rendering"},{"type":"heading","level":3,"text":"Orange","anchor":"Orange"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_radioPicker_Orange"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"heading","level":3,"text":"Orange Business Tools","anchor":"Orange-Business-Tools"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_radioPicker_OrangeBusinessTools"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"heading","level":3,"text":"Sosh","anchor":"Sosh"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_radioPicker_Sosh"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"heading","level":3,"text":"Wireframe","anchor":"Wireframe"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_radioPicker_Wireframe"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"aside","name":"Since","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"0.14.0","type":"text"}]}],"style":"note"}]}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudsradiopicker"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"kind":"sy